{"id":1875,"date":"2019-05-06T15:49:05","date_gmt":"2019-05-06T08:49:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=1875"},"modified":"2019-05-06T16:20:14","modified_gmt":"2019-05-06T09:20:14","slug":"huong-dan-cach-xem-huong-nha-khi-mua-chung-cu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/huong-dan-cach-xem-huong-nha-khi-mua-chung-cu","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, khi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea1n h\u1eb9p th\u00ec chung c\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p kh\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n nghi. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <strong>Thietkethicongdn.com<\/strong> xin h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/huong-dan-cach-xem-huong-nha-khi-mua-chung-cu\"><em><strong>c\u00e1ch xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/span> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng ri\u00eang t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1876 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/H\u01b0\u1edbng-d\u1eabn-c\u00e1ch-xem-h\u01b0\u1edbng-nh\u00e0-khi-mua-chung-c\u01b0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"428\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0 v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; V\u1edbi nh\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t, ch\u00fang ta d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ea5t, h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u0103n nh\u00e0. C\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ngo\u1ea1i vi nh\u01b0: H\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u00f3, h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi, h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u00f4ng, n\u00fai, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ed9&#8230; c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. Vi\u1ec7c xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 phong th\u1ee7y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. H\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, khi c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>H\u01b0\u1edbng chung c\u1ee7a t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/li>\n<li>H\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/li>\n<li>H\u01b0\u1edbng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch &#8211; ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp &#8211; ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 &#8211; ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/li>\n<li>H\u01b0\u1edbng thang m\u00e1y chung c\u1ee7a t\u00f2a nh\u00e0<\/li>\n<li>H\u01b0\u1edbng thang tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Do v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, bu\u1ed9c gia ch\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 c\u0103n c\u1ee9 v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1877 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/H\u01b0\u1edbng-d\u1eabn-c\u00e1ch-xem-h\u01b0\u1edbng-nh\u00e0-khi-mua-chung-c\u01b01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"442\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam:\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/kinh-nghiem-chon-xac-dinh-huong-nha-hop-tuoi\">Kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ecdn &#8211; x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 h\u1ee3p tu\u1ed5i<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0 h\u1ee3p phong th\u1ee7y<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Gi\u1eefa nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n theo nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc chung c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 theo phong th\u1ee7y nh\u00e0 \u1edf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 sao cho \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c lu\u1ed3ng kh\u00ed, lu\u1ed3ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c h\u01b0\u1edbng h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gia ch\u1ee7.<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 phong th\u1ee7y nh\u01b0: C\u1ea7u thang, ph\u00f2ng r\u00e1c, khu v\u1ec7 sinh chung&#8230;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Theo nguy\u00ean l\u00fd b\u1ea5t bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean, c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 xem h\u01b0\u1edbng khi mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9: C\u1eeda ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u01a1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea1p c\u00e1c lu\u1ed3ng kh\u00ed, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn c\u0103n h\u1ed9 sao cho h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7.<\/li>\n<li>C\u00e1ch th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng ban c\u00f4ng, ho\u1eb7c khu v\u1ef1c c\u00f3 View r\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9: Nhi\u1ec1u phong th\u1ee7y s\u01b0 tin r\u1eb1ng, khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3n n\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3n gi\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9, l\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea1p kh\u00ed ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu, n\u00ean c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng c\u0103n chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh b\u00ed b\u00e1ch, ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00f3.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1878 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/H\u01b0\u1edbng-d\u1eabn-c\u00e1ch-xem-h\u01b0\u1edbng-nh\u00e0-khi-mua-chung-c\u01b02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"428\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 2 c\u00e1ch tr\u00ean tuy kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nguy\u00ean l\u00fd b\u1ea5t bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a phong th\u1ee7y trong xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0: Ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00f3n t\u00e0i kh\u00ed, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng chung c\u01b0 x\u1ea5u. H\u00e3y d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0&gt;&gt;&gt; \u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1:\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/huong-dan-cach-hoa-giai-nha-chung-cu-khong-hop-huong\">C\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p h\u01b0\u1edbng<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, khi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea1n h\u1eb9p th\u00ec chung c\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p kh\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n nghi. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Thietkethicongdn.com xin h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch xem h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00e0 khi mua chung c\u01b0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1876,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1875"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1875"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1875\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1887,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1875\/revisions\/1887"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1876"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1875"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1875"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1875"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}